{"tid":1608611,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1857 警方：全港多區有暴動行為","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T13:46:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":16,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"82999dbfae2b5792926fcff11dc0ae824437df6f","tid":1608611,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"全港多區有暴動行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  現時在港九新界有多區有暴動的行為，暴徒在各區放火及大肆破壞，已經有多人受傷。警方緊急呼籲所有市民應該留在安全地方，切勿外出，留意最新狀況。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年10月1日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間18時57分"},{"pid":"749cc7ef76e2d296cf324932a47200e6d5659298","tid":1608611,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/01/P2019100100631.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F01%2FP2019100100631.htm&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9Ucscdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=0bc72aba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/01/P2019100100631.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3fd3b517e6c54224e64684e5d0257aead340ff92","tid":1608611,"uid":176894,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"戒嚴啦仆街"},{"pid":"fa4b80d970703fc6191e680975d70bb10f0b5c8e","tid":1608611,"uid":129739,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"其實贏左，我以為警察會講係「叛亂」"},{"pid":"19131f0b834f83ae59c454b6e9a983a5c1198815","tid":1608611,"uid":2455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"戒嚴未"},{"pid":"a07c1930539d09bb889a5393ed0934da62cb9ac7","tid":1608611,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"黑警暴動"},{"pid":"ccfe7f2d465e244407f9e579fc562cbbb9923e4f","tid":1608611,"uid":287433,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:01:46